  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">UNES:Renewable energy research</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. Research. 
2. Meetings with stakeholders. 
3. Presentation of research.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Christian Aid will work with established local and regional partners across Africa, Asia, Latin America and the Caribbean to produce clear national and regional evidence for the case for a shift to low-carbon energy, including feasible means of making this transition. This evidence will be used as the basis of building national and regional advocacy movements to deliver targeted engagement with the drivers of change, including governments, multilateral banks and regional bodies. The overarching campaign objective is to support a global shift in investment towards low-carbon energy which reduces energy poverty for the world&#x2019;s poorest nations.</narrative>
  </description>
